metadata.name: Voodoo in Africa
metadata.description:
The word voodoo originates from the word 'vodoun' in the Gbe language. It means spirit or religion.

The drumming gets faster until someone enteres into a trance.

The dusted man – the spirit medium then cooperates by dancing to drumbeats and responding to priest‘s whistling.


**This NFT is offered on a behalf of the award-winning Slovakian photographer Silvia Vaculikova (http://www.silvia-foto.sk/en/)

Together wIth the NFT itself you will acquire also the physical print in a frame (size 75x50 cm) with a signature and personal note to you.
